Strategy_resp: I tried to think of common animals that are seen in the US or else kept as pets. Then I tried to recall those typically seen in zoos, followed by those well known in other parts of the world.

I thought of popular fields of study that have existed for some time and that are usually admired.Following that, I thought of occupations that are currently at the forefront of today's society and during the pandemic.
I thought of sports that I have played or know people who play, then I considered Olympic sports.
I tried to remember things that I kept in my own garage when I had one. Then I tried to recall things I had seen in the garages of others such as friends and family members.
I tried to remember things I tend to see when staying at hotels.
I pictured myself at my last restaurant visit and tried to hone in on items that I could recall seeing or touching and using.
I thought of words that initially came to me and then tried to link with words in similar categories.
I thought of random words and then worked  in related words to those.
I thought of random words, then worked through alphabet for second letter of s words, adding related words as I went along.
